name: Megalopolis
summary: The highly anticipated trailer for Francis Ford Coppola's upcoming film 'Megalopolis' has sparked controversy after allegations that it featured fabricated quotes from renowned movie critics. Several reputable outlets, including Vulture, Variety, and the Hollywood Reporter, have reported that the trailer attributed quotes to critics who never made them. This has led to Lionsgate, the studio behind the film, pulling the trailer and issuing an apology, acknowledging that they "screwed up." The incident has cast a shadow over the promotion of 'Megalopolis,' raising questions about the film's marketing strategy and potential impact on its critical reception.

name: Ben Affleck
summary: Jennifer Lopez has filed for divorce from Ben Affleck, citing irreconcilable differences. The couple had no prenuptial agreement in place. Sources close to the couple say that Affleck showed no interest in repairing their marriage, leading Lopez to decide to move on. Their children are reportedly taking the news well. The divorce comes after two years of marriage and a decade-long on-and-off relationship. Lopez and Affleck first started dating in 2002 and became engaged the following year, but they called off their wedding just days before the ceremony. They rekindled their romance in 2021 and married in July 2022. Lopez is currently promoting her new film, "Shotgun Wedding," while Affleck is working on his upcoming movie, "The Flash."

name: Theo Von
summary: Former President Donald Trump recently sat down for an interview with comedian Theo Von, during which he engaged in a bizarre conversation about cocaine and drug use. Trump repeatedly asked Von about his experiences with cocaine, inquiring about its effects and comparing it to other stimulants. He also falsely claimed that fentanyl is not an opioid and discussed his own family's history with addiction. The interview sparked controversy and criticism, with some commentators expressing concern about Trump's apparent lack of knowledge about drug abuse and addiction. Despite the off-putting nature of the conversation, some observers suggested that Trump's willingness to engage with Von may have helped him connect with younger voters and voters who appreciate his uninhibited communication style.

name: Ella Emhoff
summary: Ella Emhoff, stepdaughter of vice presidential candidate Kamala Harris, has garnered significant media attention during the Democratic National Convention (DNC). News outlets have highlighted her presence at the event, speculating on her potential speaking role and noting her support for her stepmother. Articles have also delved into Emhoff's background as a multidisciplinary artist and her fashion choices, including her now-viral camouflage hat. Additionally, her father, Doug Emhoff, has been featured in the news, and Emhoff's children refer to Harris as "mom," underscoring the close family bonds within the Harris-Emhoff household.

name: Borderlands 4
summary: Following the announcement at Gamescom 2024, developer Gearbox has confirmed that "Borderlands 4" will be released for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S, and PC in 2025. A teaser trailer was unveiled, revealing the game's title and release window. However, Gearbox has denied rumors that the trailer hints at the return of Handsome Jack, a popular villain from previous "Borderlands" games. Despite a mixed reception due to its timing, the announcement has generated excitement among fans, with the full reveal expected to provide more details about the game's setting, characters, and gameplay.

name: Angela Alsobrooks
summary: Maryland Senate candidate Angela Alsobrooks has gained significant attention at the Democratic National Convention. In her speech, she emphasized her close relationship with Kamala Harris and praised her as a mentor and friend. Alsobrooks recounted a meeting with Harris where she was impressed by Harris's pragmatic approach to policy. Notably, Alsobrooks is seeking to become Maryland's first Black senator. Her DNC speech highlighted her underdog status in the race, but she has since gained momentum and is now a serious contender for the position.
